strings.jetkarmabot.award.errbadusername: I don't know who that is.
strings.jetkarmabot.award.errawardbot: I am a bot, and have no use for your foolish fake internet points.
strings.jetkarmabot.award.help: Awards/revokes an award to a user.
strings.jetkarmabot.award.awardtypehelp: The award to grant to/strip of the specified user
strings.jetkarmabot.status.help: Shows the amount of awards that you have
strings.jetkarmabot.status.awardtypehelp: The awardtype to show. If empty shows everything.
strings.jetkarmabot.changelocale.errorall: I would like to speak all languages at once, but because of the rules of the universe, I am not allowed to do that.
strings.jetkarmabot.changelocale.toomany:
I don't know what dialect you want me to speak in.
I know these:
strings.jetkarmabot.changelocale.localehelp: The locale to switch to. Can be "list" to list all possible locales. Also can be empty to get current locale
strings.jetkarmabot.help.help: Displays help text for all(one) command(s)
strings.jetkarmabot.help.commandhelp: The command to return help text for. If empty shows all commands.
strings.jetkarmabot.leaderboard.help: Shows the people with the most of a specific award.
strings.jetkarmabot.leaderboard.awardtypehelp: The awardtype to show a leaderboard for.
